# Cloudflare Pages headers — Phronesis Navigator.
# v2.4 code-staleness fix: always revalidate the HTML entry so a deploy's NEW FEATURES appear without a
# hard refresh (Ctrl+Shift+R). This is distinct from the DATA-staleness fix (the no-store deliverable_board
# fetch in index.html). no-cache = revalidate-before-use (304 when unchanged), not "never store".
# Inline JS/CSS ride in index.html, so revalidating it covers code too; images keep their default caching.
/
  Cache-Control: no-cache
/index.html
  Cache-Control: no-cache
